title: E120 IS LOGAN PAUL READY FOR HIS FIRST PROFESSIONAL FIGHT AGAINST KSI? - IMPAULSIVE EP. 120
itunes:title: IS LOGAN PAUL READY FOR HIS FIRST PROFESSIONAL FIGHT AGAINST KSI? - IMPAULSIVE EP. 120
description:
Boxing promoter Eddie Hearn stated that no YouTubers will be on the undercard of KSI v. Logan Paul 2. What does it take to become a professional boxer? Also, Spencer recaps his visit to Brazil and explains how we can save the Amazon Rainforest from burning to a crisp. Greg Paul is still coming atcha, but not as aggressively. AND... are humans inherently selfish?
